One Move Captures White (4)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b Black to Play.\b0
\par White has just captured three black stones with \'a1\'e2. This seems to declare that white is alive.
\par
\par However, is white's group alive as it stands? White's shape seems short of liberties...
\par }
