Diagram 1 (Giving up)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If this were a real game, it is likely that both players might have thought white was alive in the corner.
\par
\par In that case, black can only think to playing dansu at 1.
\par
\par Even if black waited until there was a pae, and played 1 as a pae threat, it is still a big mistake.
\par }
