Diagram 2 (Correct)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}{\f1\fmodern\fprq2\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It is brilliant for black to kill white by adding a stone to his dead group with 1. This is a very clever sacrifice technique. Black's dead shape is called a bulky four.
\par
\par \pard\nowidctlpar\qj It must shock white to not be able to play \b\f1 A\b0\f0 . That is what's terrifying about a shortage of liberties. This move is not easy to find.
\par }
